<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Application Shortlisted</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
        <h2 style="color: #27ae60;">Congratulations! Your Application Has Been Shortlisted</h2>
        <p>Hello {{seekerName}},</p>
        <p>Great news! Your application has been shortlisted for the following position:</p>
        <div style="background-color: #d4edda; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #27ae60;">
            <p><strong>Job Title:</strong> {{jobTitle}}</p>
            <p><strong>Company:</strong> {{providerName}}</p>
            <p><strong>Location:</strong> {{jobLocation}}</p>
        </div>
        <p>The employer will contact you shortly with further details.</p>
        <p>Best of luck!<br>WorkNow Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

